Any questions?

   Do I have to enter my bank details before a Sellsy trial?
   No, your 15-day trial is totally free and registration requires no
   credit card.
     __________________________________________________________________

   What happens at the end of my trial?
   During your 15-day free trial, you can enable your official Sellsy
   account at any time. After allotted time, a first payment will be
   required to access your account.
     __________________________________________________________________

   I would like a demonstration instead of a trial.
   No problem, you can request a demonstration here, a member of our team
   will contact you to schedule a 30-minute online appointment.
     __________________________________________________________________

   Can I add other users during subscription?
   Of course! From the settings, create accesses for your colleagues by
   simply entering their and email address; they will receive an
   invitation instantly.
     __________________________________________________________________

   Where is my data stored?
   Sellsy is hosted on our own dedicated platform, in a datacenter with
   redundant connections to the world’s leading operators. Our servers are
   managed by Claranet, a recognized hosting specialist. All your data is
   backed up every night by three independent servers.
     __________________________________________________________________

   Is support included in my contract?
   Our teams are available from 9am to 6pm CES, Monday to Friday, to
   answer you via our chat (accessible at the bottom left of your screen).
   You can also send us an email at contact@sellsy.com.
     __________________________________________________________________

   When do I have to pay for my subscription?
   Sellsy offers you two types of default payments: monthly or annual.
   Choose the option that suits you when you validate your subscription.
     __________________________________________________________________

   Can I give access to my accountant?
   Accounting access is included in your offer, in addition to the number
   of users on your account. All you have to do is contact us (by chat or
   at contact@sellsy.com) and we will send you their login details.
     __________________________________________________________________

